{
  "stem": "22652.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at the time-- at the time that-- when there was no war and I had spent the summer there for a few weeks, it worked out well.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when I went there to stay, it was hell.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I, I became an abused child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so what happened is I got news.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother wrote to me that she had been arrested.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She kept in touch with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And her plan had been to go to the free zone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "France was divided into a free and occupied zone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was caught.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was caught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I found out later on from one of her friends after the war that she and her friend were planning to go together to, to the free zone.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on that day, [SOBBING] her girlfriend said, I just have a feeling it's not going to work out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just have an omen about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Let's do it another time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my mother said, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That-- the dies are cast, I'm going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my mother went alone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so she was caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we don't know if-- you know, in the movie, they show those refugees, they latest one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Those refugees desperately tried to get to the border, Switzerland or the free zone.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the guide turns them in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So to this day, we don't know if the guide turned her in, turned them in, or if it just was-- just things went wrong.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so my mother wrote to me that she had been arrested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've always had a, a-- well, I guess, like a thought in my soul about wrong decisions, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She should have listened to her girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Her girlfriend, later on, went by herself and made it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
